{"title":"天涯之晨","authors":["洪三泰"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯之晨（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪三泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺一夜沙滩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等天涯之晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等来天涯日出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪尖上一尊太阳神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘海南炽热的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘太阳热切的眼神——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凉的风热的风馨香的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的浪白的沙乳白的云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的梦已经醒来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘一缕晨光飞动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯很近很近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯就在晨光之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原始森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我读一读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这绿叶喧喧的哲学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷帙浩繁全是人生——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于集体与自我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于生死和爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞杀树已把绿楠绞成腐木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断肠果夺去野鹿的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不想卒读这一页"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲愤和仇恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊金凤和檀香永结良缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讥笑藤缠树的虚假爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小苗都有自己的空间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春笋竞发栋梁入云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光很年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨很抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用蓬勃解析生活的哲理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色才是生命的精英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个竞争向上的主题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永驻原始森林"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}